***********************************************************************
* INSTALL: run the following commands in your terminal                *
***********************************************************************
make

***********************************************************************
* TEST OF INSTALLATION: run the following command in your terminal    *
***********************************************************************
./rubik_2^3 -c -s 1

and you should see the following output

Goal: to build at most 1 levels of single-direction quarter turns
Level  0 out of 1 finished.       1 new turns found!
Level  1 out of 1 finished.       3 new turns found!
-----------------------------------------------------------
A total of 4 turns were found within 2 families
      1 turn(s) corresponding to 
      3 turn(s) corresponding to 4^3
--------------------------------------------------------
      4 turn(s) corresponding to the families altogether

